CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in New Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, January 12, 1963, pg. 8 reads: "Green Link Golf Club - Members of the smart Green Link Golf Club entertained at a gala Pre-New Year's Masked Ball at the exclusive Green Oaks Country Club last Sunday. Posing prettily for the photographer, they are (left to right) Adeline Harris, Vera Boulden, Louis Hinton, Dorothy Gardin, Helen Peay, Helen Dyer, Arthella Everhart, Rebecca Askewe [Askew], Kathleen Cunningham, Gloria Grate, Maude Jones, Edna Stevenson and Lorraine Tillman.  Members not pictured: Altha Blair, Celorna Burton, Ella Smart and Kathleen Fitts. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of Green Link Golf Club members, from left: Adeline "Nu Nu" Harris, Vera Boulden, Louis Hinton, Dorothy Gardin, Helen Peay, Helen Dyer, Arthella Everhart, Rebecca Askew, Kathleen Cunningham, Gloria Golden Grate, Maude Jones, Edna Stevenson and Lorraine Tillman, posed in line in Green Oaks Country Club during Green Link Golf Club's Masked Ball
